Package xdc.services.getset

Class Summary
AutoFxn A Fxn that automatically determines its own inputs and outputs.
Field An immutable object that identifies a specific field of a specific XDCscript object.
Fxn A scheduled function in a Group.
GetSet A helper class to add getters and setters to a field of an XDCscript object.
GetSetData Private data for the getters and setters.
Getters A getter function to be added to a field of an XDCscript Value.Obj object.
Group A group of Fxns that are each run to completion before any other Fxn in the group.
Scheduler Schedules execution of Fxns and Groups.
Setters A setter function to be added to a field of an XDCscript Value.Obj object.
